                <ownedComment xmi:id="_16_5_4_940029b_1469893677014_419387_6649" body="&lt;para>Das Element (globales Element gml:Point) enthält die GML-Darstellung eines Punktes auf der Erdoberfläche.&lt;/para>&#xA;&#xA;&lt;para>Aus der GML-Dokumentation: &quot;A Point is defined by a single coordinate tuple. The direct position of a point is specified by the pos element which is of type DirectPositionType.&quot; Quelle: &lt;link xmlns:xlink=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink&quot; xlink:href=&quot;http://www.datypic.com/sc/niem21/e-gml32_Polygon.html&quot;>http://www.datypic.com/sc/niem21/e-gml32_Point.html&lt;/link>  &lt;/para>&#xA;" annotatedElement="_16_5_4_940029b_1469888707373_227948_6481"/>
              </ownedAttribute>
